abstract: The financial dominance of the National Rifle Association was topped by gun control groups that helped win the House for Democrats.
snippet: The financial dominance of the National Rifle Association was topped by gun control groups that helped win the House for Democrats.
lead_paragraph: Amid a numbing succession of mass shootings, gun control groups outspent the National Rifle Association in the midterm election cycle, federal filings and additional reporting indicate, upending the usual order in the partisan battle over gun use.

abstract: The deal reached between Gov. Andrew M. Cuomo, Mayor Bill de Blasio and Amazon was constructed to blunt the veto power of local politicians.
snippet: The deal reached between Gov. Andrew M. Cuomo, Mayor Bill de Blasio and Amazon was constructed to blunt the veto power of local politicians.
lead_paragraph: The deal to bring Amazon to Long Island City, at a cost of more than $2 billion in government incentives, has sparked outrage in many corners of New York City, particularly in Queens, where residents and elected officials have vowed resistance.

abstract: The Bay Area in California remains the nation’s high-tech epicenter. But New York’s tech work force has been growing impressively.
snippet: The Bay Area in California remains the nation’s high-tech epicenter. But New York’s tech work force has been growing impressively.
lead_paragraph: In 2003, Craig Nevill-Manning, a computer scientist at Google, wanted to set up an engineering outpost in New York. Google’s top leaders were skeptical, but they told him that he could go ahead if he could find 15 “Google-worthy” software developers in the city.

abstract: The cabinet’s support relieves some of the pressure on Prime Minister Theresa May, but there are several steps before the agreement could take effect.
snippet: The cabinet’s support relieves some of the pressure on Prime Minister Theresa May, but there are several steps before the agreement could take effect.
lead_paragraph: Prime Minister Theresa May’s cabinet approved a draft agreement on Britain’s withdrawal from the European Union during an emergency meeting on Wednesday, a crucial and perilous step, as the time left to strike a final deal runs short.
